Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: validatish
Version: 0.5.1
Summary: Validatish is a minimal library of validators that can be used in functional and class generated forms.
Home-page: http://ish.io/projects/show/validatish
Author: Tim Parkin, Matt Goodall
Author-email: developers@ish.io
License: BSD
Description: Validatish is a simple validation library designed to be a good building block for validation structures. It implements some basic validators in functional form (i.e. simple function calls) or in class form (i.e. instantiate a class and then just call the validate method).
        
Keywords: validation,schema,forms,form library,form
